


welcome(1)	    UNIX Programmer's Manual	       welcome(1)



NAME
     welcome - prints out a nice welcome message with useful
     statistics

SYNTAX
     welcome

DESCRIPTION
     The command makes a graphic box over box and prints out the
     time, day, and system stats

     assumes that the file /etc/motd exists.

SEE ALSO
     /etc/motd

